{FLOWER ARRANGING}
You have to take your own flowers and buy some oasis and a dish to put them in. There are two ladies to help you arrange your flowers and you can buy some ribbon. The cost of the oasis is 15p and the dishes are 15p. We go on a Monday and we have competitions at Christmas. There are different groups for their ages.
{BROWNIES}
You are allowed to go when you are 7-11. You can make things and you can get badges like 'The Pet Lovers' which means you look after your pet. They go out for trips. At the end they say pow-wow.
